l/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:12:28.000Z","msg":"建制派：<br />\n工聯會<br />\n民建聯<br />\n民主黨<br />\n公民黨"},{"pid":"97ecdc5a1fc8c9994c326e00f25171f71f2324e3","tid":930833,"uid":20924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1249704e50e75dc98fcd89949287b20162c8e2b4","tid":930833,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"阿鼎真係好為得香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e491980ffe8ba517cb6ac1e128991b10c3dbe712","tid":930833,"uid":15880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"香港一國兩制維持良好呀<br />\n<br />\n因為質疑一國兩制既人都比我地民建聯排出體制外<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提議會功能都比我地廢埋, 所以一國兩制運作良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ba7f4f192d7cc57fd4f382f5e61700434c3be3","tid":930833,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69912282dcf29ba1ccea33d99526bce2419a44f","tid":930833,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"OK, 同泛民立場差唔多"},{"pid":"2ded56d74ae4a433106c4969b1b075eae182a60a","tid":930833,"uid":37413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"當美國人白痴，你以為蛇齋餅糭嗰啲阿婆咁易呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你哋民建聯有咩劣行一定都一清二楚"},{"pid":"2e0370707b8f9b975ceb4427aa866490f89c57fa","tid":930833,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T15:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc3b667868de273dd42dad5bbdbea6d0ddc00f1","tid":930833,"uid":1372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201